  "texts": [
    "Democracies will always be particularly vulnerable to this sort of interference due to rights, such as freedom of speech, that exist in many countries.",
    "However, there are several ways that democracies can build resilience, which are outlined in the summary for policymakers (SFP2025.1).Finally, the database's insights on political parties and candidates that employ GenAI also have relevant implications.",
    "In one quarter of instances, these actors (political candidates and parties) were behind the employment of GenAI.",
    "In 38% of these cases, the IPIE deems these GenAI usages to be for ostensibly good purposes.",
    "This data underlines the necessity of finding out how GenAI might be helpful for democratizing political campaigning, such as through assisting underserved communities to be better represented on a national level."
  ]
